      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 63 judgment</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 63 judgment</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>既濟，亨，小利貞，初吉終亂。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Ji Ji intimates progress and success in small matters. There will be advantage in being firm and correct. There has been good fortune in the beginning; there may be disorder in the end.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
