      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 63 初九</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 63 初九</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>初九：曳其輪，濡其尾，无咎。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The first NINE, undivided, (shows its subject as a driver) who drags back his wheel, (or as a fox) which has wet his tail. There will be no error.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
