      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 63 六二</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 63 六二</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六二：婦喪其茀，勿逐，七日得。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The second SIX, divided, (shows its subject as) a wife who has lost her (carriage-)screen. There is no occasion to go in pursuit of it. In seven days she will find it.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
