      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 63 九三</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九三：高宗伐鬼方，三年克之，小人勿用。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The third NINE, undivided, (suggests the case of) K?o ?ung, who attacked the Demon region, but was three years in subduing it. Small men should not be employed (in such enterprises).</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
