      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六四：繻有衣袽，終日戒。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fourth SIX, divided, shows its subject with rags provided against any leak (in his boat), and on his guard all day long.</seg>
