      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 63 九五</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九五：東鄰殺牛，不如西鄰之禴祭，實受其福。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fifth NINE, undivided, shows its subject (as) the neighbour in the east who slaughters an ox (for his sacrifice); but this is not equal to the (small) spring sacrifice of the neighbour in the west, whose sincerity receives the blessing.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
